>> Title: Glance v2 API unrestricted path traversal
>> Reporter: Masahito Muroi (NTT)
>> Products: Glance
>> Versions: up to 2014.1.3 and 2014.2 version up to 2014.2.1
>>
>> Description: Masahito Muroi from NTT reported a vulnerability in 
